                        <li>In such situations, however, we will still respond to let you know of our decision. As used herein, &ldquo;Personal Information&rdquo; means any information that identifies you as an individual, such as name, address, email address, IP address, phone number, business address, business title, business email address, company, etc.&nbsp;</li>
                        <li>To make any of the following requests, please contact us (i) via email at <a href="mailto:privacy@aumet.me">privacy@aumet.me</a>, or (ii) by writing to us at Aumet, Inc., 3260 Hillview Avenue, Palo Alto, California 94304.</li>
                        <ol style="list-style-type: lower-roman;">
