                    <p><strong><strong>12.YOUR CALIFORNIA PRIVACY RIGHTS</strong></strong></p>
                    <p>Aumet&nbsp;does not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer to outside third parties your &ldquo;<u>Personal Information</u>&rdquo; as the term is defined under the California Civil Code Section &sect; 1798.82(h). Additionally, California Civil Code Section &sect; 1798.83 permits Users of our Website&nbsp;that are California&nbsp;residents to request certain information regarding our disclosure of their Personal Information to third parties&nbsp;for their direct marketing purposes. To make a request for such disclosure, or identification and/or deletion of Personal Information in all our systems that we store on you, please send an email to <a href="mailto:privacy@aumet.me">privacy@aumet.me</a> or write us at Aumet, Inc., 3260 Hillview Avenue, Palo Alto, California 94304, United States.</p>
                    <p>Note that (i) if we delete your Personal Information as requested, we will no longer be able to provide our services to you and (ii) we may need to keep such Personal Information for a while during the shutting down and billing process. If you would like to discuss our Personal Information storage and processing process with us, please send us an email at <a href="mailto:privacy@aumet.me">privacy@aumet.me</a> or write us at Aumet, Inc., 3260 Hillview Avenue, Palo Alto, California 94304, United States.</p>
                    <p><strong><strong>13.COPPA COMPLIANCE (FOR CHILDREN UNDER 13 USERS ONLY)</strong></strong></p>
                    <p>The Children&rsquo;s Online Privacy Protection Act (&ldquo;<u>COPPA</u>&rdquo;) is a federal legislation that applies to entities that collect and store &ldquo;Personal Information,&rdquo; as the term is defined under COPPA, from children under the age of 13. We are committed to ensure compliance with COPPA. Our Website are not meant for use by children under the age of 13. Our Website do not target children under the age of 13, but we do not age-screen or otherwise prevent the collection, use, and personal disclosure of persons identified as under 13. If you would like to know more about our practices and specifically our practices in relation to COPPA compliance, please email us at <a href="mailto:privacy@aumet.me">privacy@aumet.me</a>.&nbsp;</p>
                    <p>IF YOU ARE UNDER 13, PLEASE DO NOT ACCESS OR USE OUR WEBSITE.</p>
